folder: New Lots Avenue & Church Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: New Lots Avenue - Church Avenue
text:
(1)
New Lots Road, at Church Ave. (Road now non existent). This home if now in existence would occupy the intersection at Rockaway Parkway and Church Ave. It was known as the Derrick Remsen House.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
The same, showing farm in rear.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2) NEG. # 4372
